data.description: Calling all INVESTORS!!! This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home is waiting for you to fix her up! New roof and gutters in 2017. HVAC (furnace and AC), hot water heater and insulation was all updated in 2016. New rear sewer line in 2020. This home is just waiting for some TLC. The rooms are large. There are some hardwood floors with possibly more under existing carpet and tile. This home is being sold AS IS - seller to make no repairs or municipal inspection. No Sale sign in yard.
